<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 22:06:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>猫王埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 (Elvis Presley) 的亲属提起诉讼，阻止出售格雷斯兰 (Graceland) 别墅</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elvis-presley-kin-sues-to-block-sale-of-graceland-house/articleshow/110312890.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110312890.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 20:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elvis-presley-kin-sues-to-block-sale-of-graceland-house/articleshow/110312890.cms</guid></item><item><title>西方裂痕公开：法国支持国际刑事法院对比比的搜查令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/west-rift-in-open-france-backs-icc-warrant-bid-against-bibi/articleshow/110312853.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110312853.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;比利时、斯洛文尼亚和法国周一均表示支持国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗的决定，卡里姆·汗指控以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡、其国防部长和三名哈马斯领导人在加沙地带和以色列犯有战争罪和反人类罪。虽然没有人面临迫在眉睫的逮捕，但这一声明加深了以色列在全球的孤立，而此时以色列正因加沙战争而面临越来越多的批评，甚至是其最亲密盟友的批评。三个欧盟国家对逮捕令的支持也暴露了西方对以色列态度的分歧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/west-rift-in-open-france-backs-icc-warrant-bid-against-bibi/articleshow/110312853.cms</guid></item><item><title>在加沙南部城市拉法的供应耗尽后，联合国停止了在拉法的所有粮食分发</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-halts-all-food-distribution-in-rafah-after-running-out-of-supplies-in-the-southern-gaza-city/articleshow/110312768.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110312768.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;自从以色列军队两周前开始对拉法发动强化袭击以来，联合国尚未具体说明有多少人留在拉法，但显然仍有数十万人留守。世界粮食计划署表示，加沙中部地区的食物也即将耗尽，数十万逃离拉法的巴勒斯坦人在混乱的逃亡中寻求庇护，搭建新的帐篷营地，或者涌入已经被以色列先前攻势摧毁的地区。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/un-halts-all-food-distribution-in-rafah-after-running-out-of-supplies-in-the-southern-gaza-city/articleshow/110312768.cms</guid></item><item><title>暴风雨给中西部地区带来了大冰雹、倾盆大雨和龙卷风。还有更多即将到来</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/storms-have-dropped-large-hail-buckets-of-rain-and-tornadoes-across-the-midwest-and-more-is-coming/articleshow/110312617.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110312617.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 19:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/storms-have-dropped-large-hail-buckets-of-rain-and-tornadoes-across-the-midwest-and-more-is-coming/articleshow/110312617.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国议员要求对公然逃避对俄罗斯制裁的行为采取行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-mps-demand-action-taken-over-blatant-evasion-of-sanctions-on-russia/articleshow/110312243.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110312243.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国议员呼吁政府对欧洲公司逃避俄罗斯制裁采取行动。英国从中国、印度和土耳其购买的来自俄罗斯石油的燃料数量激增。人们对俄罗斯石油流入英国的漏洞表示担忧。有关为乌克兰军事援助和英国向俄罗斯邻国出口提供资金的问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 18:21:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-mps-demand-action-taken-over-blatant-evasion-of-sanctions-on-russia/articleshow/110312243.cms</guid></item><item><title>塔利班占领喀布尔近三年后，土耳其航空恢复飞往阿富汗的航班</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/turkish-airlines-resumes-flights-to-afghanistan-nearly-3-years-after-the-taliban-captured-kabul/articleshow/110310142.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110310142.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿富汗塔利班政府正式宣布重启土耳其航空飞往喀布尔国际机场的航班。近三年前，该航空公司的服务因西方支持的政府倒台而停止。阿富汗交通和民航部报告称，土耳其航空首架航班于周二抵达，并受到政府官员的热烈欢迎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 15:18:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/turkish-airlines-resumes-flights-to-afghanistan-nearly-3-years-after-the-taliban-captured-kabul/articleshow/110310142.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的律师在封口费审判中搁置案件，没有传唤他出庭作证</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumps-lawyers-rest-case-in-hush-money-trial-without-calling-him-to-testify/articleshow/110309376.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110309376.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普的辩护团队周二结束了刑事封口费审判的陈述。他们选择不让美国前总统作证。特朗普的代表律师传唤了两名证人来支持他的辩护。法官胡安·梅尔坎 (Juan Merchan) 告知，陪审员定于下周二重新召开结案陈词。预计审议将于次日开始。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trumps-lawyers-rest-case-in-hush-money-trial-without-calling-him-to-testify/articleshow/110309376.cms</guid></item><item><title>塔斯社称，俄罗斯因涉嫌欺诈而逮捕第58集团军前司令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-arrests-ex-commander-of-58th-army-on-suspicion-of-fraud-tass-says/articleshow/110308575.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110308575.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 13:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-arrests-ex-commander-of-58th-army-on-suspicion-of-fraud-tass-says/articleshow/110308575.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾爆发抗议计划限制新总统权力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/protest-erupts-in-taiwan-over-plan-to-curb-new-presidents-power/articleshow/110308907.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110308907.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周二，国民党议员启动了通过一项法律的最后步骤，该法律要求赖清德总统发表年度讲话、单独出庭回答问题，并根据要求提供各种文件。该法律还允许监禁被发现向立法机关撒谎的官员，这可能会使黎智英的官员陷入法庭诉讼。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 14:05:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/protest-erupts-in-taiwan-over-plan-to-curb-new-presidents-power/articleshow/110308907.cms</guid></item><item><title>天气预报员警告巴基斯坦人在新的热浪到来之前待在室内</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/weather-forecasters-warn-pakistanis-to-stay-indoors-ahead-of-new-heat-wave/articleshow/110300023.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110300023.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/weather-forecasters-warn-pakistanis-to-stay-indoors-ahead-of-new-heat-wave/articleshow/110300023.cms</guid></item><item><title>捷克警方指控 14 人从土耳其走私</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/czech-police-charge-14-with-people-smuggling-from-turkey/articleshow/110304328.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110304328.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;捷克警方指控 14 人将 2000 多名移民从土耳其偷渡到欧洲。该团伙获利至少 200 万欧元，并没收现金、汽车和房屋。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 11:11:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/czech-police-charge-14-with-people-smuggling-from-turkey/articleshow/110304328.cms</guid></item><item><title>智利科学家通过卫星追踪火烈鸟以保护数量不断减少的火烈鸟</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chilean-scientists-track-flamingos-by-satellite-to-preserve-dwindling-population/articleshow/110304072.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110304072.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;包括吉列尔莫·库比洛斯在内的科学家正在研究智利洛斯弗拉门戈保护区火烈鸟数量的下降，以了解气候变化、采矿和生态系统变化的影响。保护工作的重点是使用卫星发射器追踪鸟类并识别脆弱的生态系统进行保护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 11:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chilean-scientists-track-flamingos-by-satellite-to-preserve-dwindling-population/articleshow/110304072.cms</guid></item><item><title>民主党、共和党和独立人士：美国大选候选人仍在投票</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/democrats-republicans-independents-candidates-still-on-ballot-for-us-elections-donald-trump-joe-biden-robert-kennedy/photostory/110301212.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110301212.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着美国为选举做准备，以下是仍在竞选该国第 47 任总统的几位候选人。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 09:56:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/democrats-republicans-independents-candidates-still-on-ballot-for-us-elections-donald-trump-joe-biden-robert-kennedy/photostory/110301212.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国首相赞扬欧盟国家推动将寻求庇护者送往第三国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/british-pm-lauds-eu-states-push-to-send-asylum-seekers-to-third-countries/articleshow/110303235.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110303235.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克在访问维也纳时对奥地利和其他 14 个欧盟国家的联名信表示赞赏，该信旨在寻找处理无证移民的“新想法”，包括将一些无证移民送往第三国。奥地利保守党总理卡尔·内哈默在与苏纳克的联合新闻声明中表示，奥地利“完全支持英国的道路”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:39:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/british-pm-lauds-eu-states-push-to-send-asylum-seekers-to-third-countries/articleshow/110303235.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国如何利用“认知战”影响全球观念</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/how-china-is-using-cognitive-warfare-to-influence-global-perceptions/articleshow/110303476.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110303476.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:53:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/how-china-is-using-cognitive-warfare-to-influence-global-perceptions/articleshow/110303476.cms</guid></item><item><title>法国总统马克龙将访问饱受骚乱影响的新喀里多尼亚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/frances-president-macron-to-visit-riot-scarred-new-caledonia/articleshow/110303148.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110303148.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴黎周二表示，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙将访问遭受骚乱影响的新喀里多尼亚，游客正在从遭受一周多动乱的太平洋领土上撤离。澳大利亚游客马克斯韦尔·温彻斯特(Maxwell Winchester)表示，他和妻子蒂芙尼在被困在一个被封锁的度假村一周后，听到撤离航班开始起飞，感到“欣喜若狂”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:37:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/frances-president-macron-to-visit-riot-scarred-new-caledonia/articleshow/110303148.cms</guid></item><item><title>从黑帮到小偷：日本黑帮老大因盗窃神奇宝贝卡而被捕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/from-gangsters-to-petty-thieves-yakuza-boss-arrested-for-stealing-pokmon-cards-in-japan/articleshow/110303361.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110303361.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/from-gangsters-to-petty-thieves-yakuza-boss-arrested-for-stealing-pokmon-cards-in-japan/articleshow/110303361.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国顶级新冠专家正在为下一次全球大流行做准备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-chinas-top-covid-expert-is-preparing-for-next-global-pandemic/articleshow/110303351.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110303351.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-chinas-top-covid-expert-is-preparing-for-next-global-pandemic/articleshow/110303351.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗人向在直升机失事中丧生的总统致以最后的敬意</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranians-pay-last-respects-to-president-killed-in-helicopter-crash/articleshow/110302080.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110302080.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;数千人哀悼在大不里士直升机失事中丧生的总统易卜拉欣·莱西及其随行人员。在全国哀悼中，棺材被抬着游行。随着阿里·哈梅内伊 (Ali Khamenei) 于 6 月 28 日宣布选举，调查仍在继续。莱西的遗体将空运到库姆，然后运往马什哈德埋葬。周日，与莱西一起飞行的另外两架直升机在恶劣天气下与他的飞机失去了联系，展开了大规模的搜救行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:12:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranians-pay-last-respects-to-president-killed-in-helicopter-crash/articleshow/110302080.cms</guid></item><item><title>北斗：中国正在推进自己的卫星导航系统，准备挑战美国的GPS</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/beidou-china-advancing-own-satellite-navigation-system-ready-to-take-on-uss-gps/articleshow/110303036.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110303036.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 10:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/beidou-china-advancing-own-satellite-navigation-system-ready-to-take-on-uss-gps/articleshow/110303036.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>